{"tid":803391,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"又一國際性黑店- Romwe","createTime":"2018-09-02T08:48:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-04T05:05:44.000Z","uid":136578,"like":6,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"33d3f41afc922f247ebb7596737fb8667b865e2a","tid":803391,"uid":136578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T08:48:03.000Z","msg":"[借朋友ac]<br />\n成日禁ig見到romwe啲廣告 又有特價咪試下幫襯<br />\n買左5樣野 唔知點解要分開兩個包裹咁寄 <br />\n一個得一件衫 另一個係嗰4件野<br />\n仲要兩個寄唔同地址 <br />\n一個寄去我hall無問題 另外嗰個要特登出去拎都算 <br />\n<br />\n一拆 盲既都知係淘寶 由大陸寄過黎 仲要比埋個成本價我 慌我唔知中撚左伏咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/02/164128_ac47d611528c7bcc5a2b04a80d50381a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F02%2F164128_ac47d611528c7bcc5a2b04a80d50381a.png&h=7daf1730&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/02/164232_a3093d3b2c11dfa8cdb4eba3e8d13a59.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F02%2F164232_a3093d3b2c11dfa8cdb4eba3e8d13a59.png&h=1b78c2ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n件衫黎到同佢description唔同 咪同佢講return 佢話差1-2cm好正常 之後我一度差5cm 影比佢睇 佢話寄返比佢 喺美國 但唔比shipping fee我 咁我咪好on9咁洩撚左錢？之後我話唔得 呢個係佢地既問題 無理由無啦啦要我洩錢 之後佢話比返一半shipping我 咁我都覺得唔可以 繼續擾攘左幾日 終於佢叫我捐左件衫佢或者送比人 再唔係就比返AU$5我收聲（件衫我AU$10買返黎）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/02/164432_d52ac79ae97c32fa820a413d6223ea24.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F02%2F164432_d52ac79ae97c32fa820a413d6223ea24.png&h=f56571a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n已經唔止係錢既問題 同埋我真係無錢 <br />\n係明明係佢錯 點解要我負呢個責任 <br />\n仲要因為佢既錯 叫我買件衫黎捐鳩左佢<br />\n<br />\n就係呢間垃圾<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/02/164518_dbd3ba8c2a2a532d6976d47c20ce5aef.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F02%2F164518_dbd3ba8c2a2a532d6976d47c20ce5aef.png&h=0e58f60e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/02/164521_1dc9f852da6b9925a8a4cf0563b57151.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F02%2F164521_1dc9f852da6b9925a8a4cf0563b57151.png&h=838cc693&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a8cb5412d41ebe5827cb832ade6234d42425e04","tid":803391,"uid":182930,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T08:49:28.000Z","msg":"邊會有人買I豬Shop架"},{"pid":"9a3d1c4896f99b5f1b491c2ed382e6b289e698c7","tid":803391,"uid":136578,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T08:49:52.000Z","msg":"事後有朋友問咩事<br />\n仲話呢間野喺youtuber口中review唔錯"},{"pid":"81a6ef8033b3c55ea1b15d6e64ab646ab2a4bc6c","tid":803391,"uid":40499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T08:58:29.000Z","msg":"幫你推下 最憎呢d仆街網店"},{"pid":"c2a66c5ae36d3bd94d70e06ea6a00c3b32336183","tid":803391,"uid":136578,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:14:16.000Z","msg":"呢間唔係igshop... 係外國既網店"},{"pid":"104fd36b7bcc1c63cb93df11c430f9266c0ae40d","tid":803391,"uid":81575,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:14:32.000Z","msg":"報澳洲海關 或類似消委會嗰D得唔得?<br />\n<br />\n澳洲唔係不問理由可以退貨架咩?<br />\n<br />\n若然經營者係澳洲人，好多嘢可同佢玩。<br />\n<br />\n若係支那人，咁你柒左啦<br />\n<br />\n而家好多呢D扮外地網實際係大陸出貨。<br />\n<br />\n基本上你識整個網，可以放佢地D貨上去，收到單，你先係大陸出貨，直寄去你個客到。"},{"pid":"74c3943f5a21171681d30291ea57597ca8f73e55","tid":803391,"uid":90471,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:18:43.000Z","msg":"正皮打氣"},{"pid":"4d9a0ae446f38220575a676196c81ca8bca162e2","tid":803391,"uid":14095,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:24:05.000Z","msg":"幾10蚊預左中國制嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俾豉油錢就想食雞脾<br />\n你俾幾錢就俾咩服務同貨你"},{"pid":"1018e7f1b55c166a504c8014d23fc6cf4c183d48","tid":803391,"uid":122816,"like":0